short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension for submit application to BorrowerCheck

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: BorrowerCheck enables auto dealers to recognize borrowers with income, employment, and identity-related risks that may result in a demand to buy back the loan from the lender or add friction to future loan applications.
